en_139639_0	Former TNA MP Podiappuhamy Piyasena was further remanded till August 5 by Colombo Fort Magistrate Lanka Jayaratne for alleged misuse of a vehicle given him by the Prime Minister's Office.
en_139639_1	The MP had requested for a vehicle in February 2015 and has allegedly failed to return it after the August 2015 general election.
en_139639_2	He was defeated in that election.
en_139639_3	A driver brought the vehicle to the Kollupitiya Police on July 28.
en_139639_4	Piyasena was arrested by the CCD the next day.
